"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-03-06-organisers-earmark-326000-tickets-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - A total of 326,000 tickets are set to be sold or given away for the opening ceremony of the Paris Olympics on the river Seine, Interior Minister Gerald Darmanin said yesterday, giving the exact number for the first time.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9872697572349916, \"rank\": 0.006788570313174413, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 149, \"end\": 166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\", \"score\": 0.9443295670895389, \"rank\": 0.05895050208637026, \"text\": \"Interior Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\"}, {\"begin\": 167, \"end\": 173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"score\": 0.9999985684756908, \"rank\": 6.785612214759179e-07, \"text\": \"Gerald\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"AFP\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 18}, {\"ngram\": \"A total\", \"from\": 22, \"to\": 29}, {\"ngram\": \"326,000 tickets\", \"from\": 33, \"to\": 48}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 86, \"to\": 106}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 128}, {\"ngram\": \"the river Seine\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 147}, {\"ngram\": \"the exact number\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 222}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers have scaled back their plans for the waterborne parade - with crowds once imagined as large as two million people - in the face of resistance from French security services and worries about terror attacks.\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 402, \"end\": 408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9602468613454284, \"rank\": 0.03289905148000611, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 254}, {\"ngram\": \"their plans\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"the waterborne parade\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 309}, {\"ngram\": \"crowds\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 323}, {\"ngram\": \"two million people\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 368}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 382}, {\"ngram\": \"resistance\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 396}, {\"ngram\": \"worries\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 438}, {\"ngram\": \"terror attacks\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it is still set to break records in terms of size, with all previous opening ceremonies taking place in the main athletics stadium.\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"records\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"size\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"all previous opening ceremonies\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"the main athletics stadium\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will have 104,000 spectators on the lower bank who have paid for a ticket,\\\" Darmanin told a hearing in the Senate.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 710, \"end\": 716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Senate\", \"score\": 0.597719255008356, \"rank\": 0.6727448047362763, \"text\": \"Senate\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Senate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Senate\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"104,000 spectators\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"the lower bank\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"a ticket\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"Darmanin\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"a hearing\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then you have 222,000 people on the higher banks [with free tickets].\\\"\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"222,000 people\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"the higher banks\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 767}, {\"ngram\": \"free tickets\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He estimated that another 200,000 people would watch the open-air parade on July 26 on the river from buildings that overlook the Seine, with an additional 50,000 in fan zones in the capital.\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9997566391562457, \"rank\": 0.00024341686609933853, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another 200,000 people\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"the open-air parade\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 863}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"buildings\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"fan zones\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The open-air ceremony on boats is in keeping with promises to make the Paris Olympics \\\"iconic\\\", with the local organising committee keen to break from past traditions in the way it stages the world's biggest sporting event.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The open-air ceremony\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"boats\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"promises\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"the local organising committee\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"past traditions\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1150}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's biggest sporting event\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2008 Beijing Summer Olympics ceremony is generally considered to be the most spectacular in history, while the 2012 London ceremony, overseen byTrainspottingdirector Danny Boyle, won rave reviews for showcasing Britain's quirky side.\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1324, \"end\": 1335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9952253746312066, \"rank\": 0.004797530276788482, \"text\": \"2012 London\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1379, \"end\": 1390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Boyle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Danny Boyle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Boyle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Boyle\"}, {\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999774446236549, \"rank\": 9.195503036426467e-06, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2008 Beijing Summer Olympics ceremony\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"rave reviews\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A total of 180 boats are set to sail around six kilometres down the Seine, of which 94 will contain athletes, the top security official for the Paris region, Marc Guillaume, told the same hearing.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1516, \"end\": 1521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9997566391562457, \"rank\": 0.00024341686609933853, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 1592, \"end\": 1597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998312887, \"rank\": 1.6882138712705698e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A total\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1455}, {\"ngram\": \"180 boats\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"the top security official\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"Marc Guillaume\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"the same hearing\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The executive in charge of planning and risk management at the Paris organising committee toldAFPlast week that special security measures would be considered for high-risk delegations such as those from the US or Israel.\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1709, \"end\": 1714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998312887, \"rank\": 1.6882138712705698e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486